Package no.geosoft.timeseriesio.json

package no.geosoft.timeseriesio.json
  • Class
    Description
    Signal
    Model a time series signal as it is defined by the TimeSeries.JSON format.
    TimeSeriesJson
    Class representing the content of one TimeSeries.JSON entry.
    TimeSeriesJsonDataListener
    Provides a mechanism for the client to monitor and process data during a time series read operation, and also to abort the process in case that is requested by user or for other reasons.
    TimeSeriesJsonReader
    Class for reading TimeSeries.JSON files.
    TimeSeriesJsonUtil
    Utility methods for working with TimeSeries.JSON data.
    TimeSeriesJsonWriter
    Class for writing TimeSeries.JSON entries to disk.
    WellKnownProperty
    List the well known properties of the TimeSeries.JSON format.
